name: arrow
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.7.0" %}
{% set gh_org = "crsmithdev" %}
{% set gh_repo = "arrow" %}


package:
  name: {{ gh_repo }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ gh_repo }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b09bb271247f134f53fcecc8aa09395c23b04633bdd3db22e28f3efb8ccfcabc

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - python-dateutil

test:
  files:
    - requirements.txt
  requires:
    - nose
    - coverage
    - simplejson

about:
  home: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}
  license: Apache-2.0
  summary: Better dates & times for Python

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
